**Session Focus**: Strict TQL investor masking + Quinn AI experience layer + Flash Submit / 3.4 upload polish + Encompass field-305 hardening.

## Status
- **Completed:**
  - **Strict masking is live** in `api/get-ob-pricing.ts`. `maskProgramName()` strips ~25 investor brands (Ascend, Elevate, Peek, TOTAL, TPO-VRS, Deephaven, Verus, Rocket TPO, AD Mortgage, LoanStream, Planet Mortgage, Champions, Lima One, Acra, Velocity, Visio, Newrez, Citadel, Angel Oak, A&D, FOA, Quontic, Sprout, Carrington, plus pre-existing TQL prefixes) and tier suffixes (`- EG`, `- Tier N`, `- Standard/Plus/Premier/Select/Premium/Core/Prime`, `(EG)`). PPP qualifier extracted and re-emitted as `5%PPP / 3%PPP / 1%PPP / 5yrPPP / NoPPP`. Format: `TQL - <doc> <term>yr <amort>[ <ppp>]`.
  - Programs ship `name`/`programName` (masked) **plus** `rawName`/`rawInvestor`/`rawProgramName`/`rawInvestorName` (admin-only). `investor`/`investorName` forced `"TQL"`.
  - **Admin reveals raw** — passcode `TQLFAITH` (case + space insensitive) flips `showRawInvestor`. Sidebar "User Admin · Raw Investor View"; modal CTAs "Reveal Master Investor Results" / "Re-Mask · Hide Raw Investor Names".
  - Full price ladder always visible to brokers; `showFullResults` is now a constant `true`. Removed all "Hide Full Results" copy/state.
  - **Quinn AI flair**: new `<QuinnGlow>` component (glowing **Q**, Sky Signal `#38BDF8`). Hero card: `Quinn AI · Lowest Rate · Highest Price` + corner "AI Pick" chip with mini Q. Loading: "Quinn AI · Price Search…". "More Pricing Options" pill: sky-blue `AI Filtered · 99.000–101.750`.
  - Encompass field 305 (Lender Case #) — retries up to 4× with 350ms backoff reading fields 305 / 4 / 364, then writes loan number into 305 via `/fieldReader`+`/fieldWriter`. Returns 317-prefixed number, never the GUID.
  - Submit Complete page: 3 CTAs (Submit a New Loan, Go to TQLTPO Site, Log into Bench Loan Hub) + Lender Tracking # surfaced.
  - Flash Submit confirmation modal + `/api/flash-submit-request` endpoint sends PDF (pdf-lib) email from `Flash@tqltpo.com` → `disclosuredesk@tqlend.com` cc broker.
  - Email Rate Quote modal + `buildRateQuoteEmail()` (mobile-first, system-font stack, max-width 600px, viewport meta).
  - DSCR 5% PPP pinned + price-band-bypassed when Doc Type = DSCR.
  - ErrorBoundary at `<main>` root prevents blank-screen crashes.
- **Next Up:** Validate live DSCR end-to-end on `submit.tqltpo.com`; manually confirm passcode unlock (controlled-input limitation in headless tests).
- **Blockers:** None.

