## Key Rules (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
- **Investor masking is permanent.** Every broker / borrower / email / PDF / quote surface MUST display `name`. Only the admin-gated `rawName` may surface for internal audit.
- **Investor field is forced to `"TQL"`.** Never display the underlying lender brand on broker-facing surfaces.
- **Admin passcode is `TQLFAITH`** (lowercased + whitespace stripped before comparison).

## OB Channel 165481 Reference
- Accepted `incomeVerificationType` enums: `FullDoc | WrittenVOE | Stated | NoIncomeVerification | InvestorDscr` (no hyphen). Map: full → FullDoc, dscr → InvestorDscr, everything alt-doc → WrittenVOE, noRatio → NoIncomeVerification.
- Required `customFields` (else 0 products): `CustomProductFilter01..04 = '110'` mapped to `CustomLenderField4/5/7/8`.
- DSCR products require `expandedGuidelines.debtServiceCoverageRatio` populated.
- Product search returns NO LLPAs — must call detail endpoint per product:
  `GET /full/api/businesschannels/{bcId}/originators/{origId}/productsearch/{searchId}/products/{productId}` → `{ quotes[], adjustments: [{reason, adjustor (string), type}] }`. Filter quotes by `desiredLockPeriod`.

## Encompass Reference
- Token: `POST /oauth2/v1/token` with `username@encompass:{instanceId}` smart user, password grant.
- Field 305 (Lender Case #) — populate via `PATCH /encompass/v3/loans/{loanId}/fieldWriter` body `[{fieldId:"305", value:"…"}]`.
- Field 4 (Loan Number) — Encompass auto-generates 317-prefixed.
- Current creds (live in Vercel + .env.local): `ENCOMPASS_USERNAME=Jbeach`, `ENCOMPASS_PASSWORD=enPlantshop25$`, `ENCOMPASS_INSTANCE_ID=BE11223549`.

